&gt; &gt; topmost element, isn&#39;t it the same?  Or does it have to remove the
&gt; &gt; &quot;same&quot; resource every single time?  The URI points to the resource at
&gt; &gt; the top of the queue.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; If yes, is GET /currentTime idempotent given that the currentTime
&gt; &gt; changes continually?
